83
00:11:21,170 --> 00:11:21,810
Give me this piece.

84
00:11:21,810 --> 00:11:22,460
Okay.

85
00:11:23,130 --> 00:11:23,490
Take it.

86
00:11:23,490 --> 00:11:25,500
You said your waist was sprained

87
00:11:25,500 --> 00:11:27,690
