94
00:11:39,220 --> 00:11:40,350
What a coincidence.

95
00:11:40,460 --> 00:11:43,580
Madam Wang lives by doing laundry.

96
00:11:51,700 --> 00:11:52,160
Enough.

97
00:11:56,870 --> 00:11:58,420
Widow Wang is doing business.

98
00:11:58,420 --> 00:11:59,820
Can't I go to her for business?

99
00:11:59,820 --> 00:12:00,740
Of course.

100
00:12:01,910 --> 00:12:03,390
It's only ten miles bringing pigs

101
00:12:03,390 --> 00:12:05,610
from the next village.

102
00:12:05,920 --> 00:12:07,120
It's a short journey.

103
00:12:07,320 --> 00:12:10,220
Is it necessary to stop, take a shower,

104
00:12:10,220 --> 00:12:11,350
and even have a meal?

105
00:12:13,820 --> 00:12:16,880
