110
00:12:25,890 --> 00:12:27,940
No wonder you were kicked out by her.

111
00:12:28,290 --> 00:12:28,770
Done.

112
00:12:28,790 --> 00:12:29,800
Five taels of silver.

113
00:12:29,800 --> 00:12:30,860
Apply it once a day.

114
00:12:31,340 --> 00:12:32,400
