118
00:12:35,460 --> 00:12:35,790
Fine.

119
00:12:35,890 --> 00:12:37,180
It's okay if you don't want it.

120
00:12:37,180 --> 00:12:38,580
I'll ask your wife for it.

121
00:12:38,980 --> 00:12:40,420
No, I want it.

122
00:12:40,540 --> 00:12:41,260
I want it.

123
00:12:42,180 --> 00:12:42,910
Here you are.

124
00:12:43,200 --> 00:12:43,950
Here.

125
00:12:45,260 --> 00:12:45,860
Thank you.

126
00:12:51,500 --> 00:12:52,040
See you.

127
00:12:53,790 --> 00:12:54,870
This rib is nice.

128
00:12:55,100 --> 00:12:56,420
It has got both fatty and lean parts.

129
00:12:56,420 --> 00:12:58,220
I can cook a good dinner tonight.

130
00:12:59,060 --> 00:13:00,320
