159
00:14:28,490 --> 00:14:30,690
It'll be faster for him to reincarnate.

160
00:14:31,120 --> 00:14:31,620
By the way,

161
00:14:31,620 --> 00:14:32,300
I'm sorry.

162
00:14:32,490 --> 00:14:34,950
I have to do bonesetting for Ironsmith Wang.

163
00:14:35,030 --> 00:14:35,740
See you.

