197
00:16:35,480 --> 00:16:37,020
Fang Duobing, it's you.

198
00:16:38,750 --> 00:16:39,560
Directors.

199
00:16:40,620 --> 00:16:41,420
We meet again.

200
00:16:44,500 --> 00:16:45,910
I knew it.

201
00:16:46,220 --> 00:16:47,950
Yuan Jiankang?

202
00:16:47,980 --> 00:16:49,240
Isn't it Fang Duobing?

203
00:16:49,270 --> 00:16:50,710
He almost got away.

204
00:16:51,120 --> 00:16:51,490
No.

205
00:16:51,620 --> 00:16:52,880
