206
00:16:54,040 --> 00:16:55,020
Why can't I come?

207
00:16:55,410 --> 00:16:56,830
I took the exam for three years in a row,

208
00:16:56,830 --> 00:16:58,090
but you always find excuses

209
00:16:58,090 --> 00:16:59,030
