219
00:17:18,430 --> 00:17:20,100
You are the only descendant

220
00:17:20,130 --> 00:17:21,890
of the Fang family and the Tianji Manor.

221
00:17:21,890 --> 00:17:22,480
We...

222
00:17:24,820 --> 00:17:26,950
Of course we are not afraid of trouble,

223
00:17:27,190 --> 00:17:29,190
but there's no need to make trouble.

224
00:17:29,620 --> 00:17:30,220
All right.

225
00:17:30,390 --> 00:17:31,920
Tie him up and send him back.

226
00:17:32,730 --> 00:17:33,280
Wait.

227
00:17:35,700 --> 00:17:37,030
Head Li asked me to come.

228
00:17:37,500 --> 00:17:38,700
Don't you even listen

229
00:17:38,700 --> 00:17:39,660
Head Li's order?

230
00:17:40,420 --> 00:17:41,119
Head Li.

231
00:17:49,180 --> 00:17:51,520
My master left me this sword.

232
00:17:52,740 --> 00:17:53,680
You should know

233
00:17:54,210 --> 00:17:55,810
