235
00:18:08,130 --> 00:18:09,130
Your master is...

236
00:18:09,300 --> 00:18:09,800
Yes.

237
00:18:10,980 --> 00:18:13,990
My master is the famous Li Xiangyi.

238
00:18:14,700 --> 00:18:17,600
And I am your Head's direct disciple.

239
00:18:28,410 --> 00:18:31,140
Li Xiangyi's Young Master Sword is the most rigid in the world.

240
00:18:31,140 --> 00:18:32,380
But few people know

241
00:18:32,860 --> 00:18:34,660
he also has a most flexible sword

242
00:18:35,130 --> 00:18:36,390
called Neck-cutting.

243
00:18:36,980 --> 00:18:38,700
My master has never

244
00:18:38,840 --> 00:18:39,900
used Neck-cutting in public.

245
00:18:39,900 --> 00:18:41,460
