253
00:18:57,220 --> 00:18:59,220
Can you take me in now?

254
00:18:59,460 --> 00:19:00,140
But...

255
00:19:00,940 --> 00:19:01,620
I...

256
00:19:11,980 --> 00:19:13,530
When Sigu Sect was in trouble,

257
00:19:13,530 --> 00:19:14,550
[Final Contract]

258
00:19:13,790 --> 00:19:15,910
