267
00:19:29,500 --> 00:19:30,300
He's not dead.

268
00:19:34,460 --> 00:19:36,820
So I want to stay in Baichuan Academy

269
00:19:37,580 --> 00:19:39,010
and wait for my master to come back

270
00:19:39,010 --> 00:19:40,410
and revive the Sigu Sect.

271
00:19:44,120 --> 00:19:44,900
Young Master.

272
00:19:44,900 --> 00:19:46,360
