273
00:19:48,770 --> 00:19:50,090
Luckily, uncle told me

274
00:19:50,110 --> 00:19:51,340
a secret of Head Li.

275
00:19:51,730 --> 00:19:52,490
Otherwise,

276
00:19:53,460 --> 00:19:54,920
I almost couldn't make it.

277
00:19:55,640 --> 00:19:57,370
Young Master, you're amazing.

278
00:19:58,140 --> 00:19:58,900
But

279
00:19:59,140 --> 00:20:00,650
if Madam knows that you pretended to be sick,

280
00:20:00,650 --> 00:20:01,860
skipped the general examination,

281
00:20:01,860 --> 00:20:03,060
